Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.17,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.88,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,うんざりだよね  だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:57.68,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,堂々と断っちゃう　キミになりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:58.88,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:02.51,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,キッパリしなきゃ　嘘に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:07.60,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,付きあってられないよ　狭い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.15,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,自分で見つけた　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.48,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,好きになって当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.94,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,くだらないやり方蹴って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:19.91,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてはあたしが決める!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.37,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.83,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,Super Driver　突進まかせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.75,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,なんてったって前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.58,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.71,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.88,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,飛び越えて　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.42,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,大勝利って同感もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.30,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どうなったって快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.01,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.38,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.43,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,それより　さあ　急いでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.06,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってムリヤリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.98,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,まるでまるで未経験　これからしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.69,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってトツゼン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:03:00.53,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,まるでまるで未経験　それがどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.17,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.88,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为无聊之极
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:57.68,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,才必须堂堂正正地拒绝　如你一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:58.88,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:02.51,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须对谎话斩钉截铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:07.60,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,在这不能相处的狭窄世界内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.15,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,发现自己　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.48,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会喜欢上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.94,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,把无聊的东西一脚踢开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:19.91,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都由我来决定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.37,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.83,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,Super Driver　随我冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.75,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,不管一切向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.58,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.71,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.88,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来飞越　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.42,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是取得大胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.30,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,无法阻挡的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.38,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.43,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个　来吧　加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.06,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个那个也还没体验　无论何时都要硬干下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.98,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全地没有经验　现在就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.69,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个那个也还没体验　无论何时都要马上行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:03:00.53,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全地没有经验　那又怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.07,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空から落ちてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:48.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}全ての願いを乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.41,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ひとつの星にはちょっと重かったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.66,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}やっぱり何かヘンだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.25,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}心のキミが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:03.62,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}確かに憶えてるって言えるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.08,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}止マレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.88,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}過去は自分のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:13.34,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}当然　誰とも取り替えたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:14.55,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}なぜなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:19.72,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}バースデイだった　私達には
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:22.69,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}出会いが生まれたときに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.06,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}初めての夢が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.03,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}どうしようかって　悩んだ事も
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:34.03,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}いま思えば笑えるほどだったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:38.87,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}もう忘れてた　キミを探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.07,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}仅仅只因从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:48.86,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}便要承担全部愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.41,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}对于一颗小小流星　是否有些沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.66,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}果然有哪里出了错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.25,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}心中你已消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:03.62,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}「没忘掉你」这话　又要怎么说出？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.08,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}停下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.88,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}过去只属于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:13.34,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}当然不会将其交给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:14.55,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:19.72,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}生日那一天　大家在此处相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:22.69,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}但在那天的初梦前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.06,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}我们早已相知相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.03,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}之前那不知如何是好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:34.03,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}此刻回想　却是那般可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:38.87,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}已经忘了吗　那来找你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个慵懒  而又正常到了极点的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盂兰盆会后的盛夏的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电视中正在播放的  是跟我一点关系都没有的同县选手的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出于对弱者的同情心  我不由得支持着正处于落后的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而这时手机却大声嚷嚷了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是春日啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两点整全员在车站前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轻描淡写地挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么就知道我今天很闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我可也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…  虽说我什么计划也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:00:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘跟你说了  带一套泳装骑车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  带上足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,打手现正悠闲地跑向三垒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.89,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,投手铃木  在投手丘上一副崩溃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是惨不忍睹的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:22.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,真凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,没人向投手铃木发出嘘声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就是8：0了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:36.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛进入了艰巨的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.42,staffbiaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,294)\fs27\an5}Endless Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.42,staffbiaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,370)\an5}漫无止境的八月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了  阿虚！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多拿点干劲出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让本团长等你  你以为自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要惩罚啦  惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明就提前了15分钟来  为什么每次都是最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  全都到齐了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉  你就载实玖瑠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和有希坐阿虚后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且问一句  去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天当然要有夏天的样子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的时间可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在就要行动  在这个只有一次的高一的暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的时间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这消毒液的气味  真给人一种实在的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来～啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（禁止跳水  危险！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧过来  水温温的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就看不见到处贴的那些禁止跳水的文字说明么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很让人欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得  凉宫同学也学会了有常识性的娱乐方法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打个电话过来  单方面地说好就挂的邀请方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不能说得上是常识性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:05:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  笑得那么开心的凉宫同学  是不会做什么震动这个世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  自从上次合宿以来  也没引起过什么让人注目的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这会儿  对凉宫同学而言也好  对我们来说也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就是和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是  实玖瑠亲手做的三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再吃一块炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠  给我倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  非常和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是市民泳池  倒是个更适合平民泳池这名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  实玖瑠你在干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种过暑假的方法倒也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些就是我的团员们  说什么都会听的  所以随便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着考虑了下今后的活动计划  如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样来度过已经所剩无几的暑假的计划表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,SOS团的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  暑假只剩下两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得还有很多事情没做呢  要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在暑假不能不做的事情…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏期合宿  游泳池  盆舞  烟花汇演  打工  天体观测…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个表上的东西要在两周之内都做完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…  我想捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么明天开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近有什么地方明天会跳盆舞么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有烟花汇演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少查过了再给我实行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去查吧  回头联系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  别忘了捞金鱼哦  这可是实玖瑠的强烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么总是我付钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你迟到了  这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可别让人等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  现在开始每天都玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天早晨  将我的懒觉夺走的又是春日打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到跳盆舞的会场了  时间是今晚  地点是市民运动场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏她能时机正好地找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中正半怀佩服时  春日说出了这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去买浴衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠和有希都说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,买一整套的话就会便宜  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日擅自为朝比奈学姐和长门挑选了以后  毫不客气地冲进了试衣间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可相当花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,期间频遭女性顾客冷眼  我们等了大约一小时  三个人终于都换好出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  都非常合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  是我给挑选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是我挑的  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  这是在春日强行加上的服装中最顶级的货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  超合适  这个给YES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（YESだね：捏自Brain Power(机动神脑)的台词）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这个国家的古典民俗衣着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然胸口有点难受  不过好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就准备好了  那么出发吧  去盆舞会场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过盆舞啊  感觉好像很久没有看到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  实玖瑠  你想要玩的捞金鱼也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捞个痛快吧  黑色凸眼金鱼可是加200分的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去玩吧  来比比看能捞多少条如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我PASS  比起那个我还是对食物有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长门你觉得如何  要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对那种东西有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,13条  虽然是大丰收但我不需要那么多  就只要了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是完全捞不起来  捞金鱼好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  正常人是捞不了那么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有诀窍的话就很简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  有希  那个面具是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,买的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗…不过为什么要这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是波长相合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为是宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一块还没转过  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只吃一个的话没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  盆舞也差不多跳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来玩烟花吧  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得穿这身  今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也对  对面的店里就有卖的  就去河边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柿崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（此处捏自「超时空要塞Macross」剧场版的柿崎机(VF-1A)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盆舞  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么明天是捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日啊  虽说玩也没问题  你暑假作业做完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说一点也没有动的我说这话有点那啥就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  那种程度的作业有三天不就全部做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我七月就解决掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种麻烦事就得事先赶紧收拾了  再毫无后顾之忧地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是正确的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这种家伙脑子这么好  上天对于人的参数调整还真是随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  明天去捉昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捉到的虫子最多的那个人…  这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就把团长的权力让给他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣呢  只要是虫子的话什么都可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…只能抓蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  这就是SOS团内部的捉蝉大战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只多抓了一只也算赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了祈雨  我把晴天娃娃用五寸钉刺着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到来的却是万里无云的好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蝉也为今年夏天最热的一天而雀跃不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  蝉能够拿来吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许弄成天妇罗会是极品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我有时会想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天妇罗会不会只是外面一层面衣好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  那蝉也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快道歉！快向全国的天妇罗店道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你让青春年华的高中生拿着虫网与笼子聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  没有虫网的话怎么抓蝉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是问那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们开始了  优胜者可以当一天的团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没在听…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的想赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  捕蝉的话  小学不都试过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊  尽力而行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经抓到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是蝉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海…海格力斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（大力神独角仙(D.hercules)，胸部有大而光滑的角）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公布结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠一只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有希四只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉七只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚九只
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后最高纪录是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  你不用说都知道是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我！十二只！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  团长之座一天都让不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家真是可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会真的想把它们做成天妇罗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么成我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  还是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放它们一条生路  以后说不定会来报恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快回山里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是说得好听  但你这只是单方面的捕捉后放生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是接着的下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日不知从何处找来了兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还难得为我们争取了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本地超市的纪念促销宣传活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工作内容是吸引顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…连我都非得装成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是暑假的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有别的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且春日只是在一旁凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下来与她的日薪要是一样的话  绝对要暴动的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于能明白脱皮后蛇的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  真是一个好例子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,店长大叔也谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要大叔的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个外套就是工钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔也看在实玖瑠的份上说送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只青蛙要放在社团室里当作纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠  你想什么时候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我许可的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池  盂兰盆节  捕虫  兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后春日进行的就是天体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  这就是这个年代的望远镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与开普勒时代的没什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我觉得相差很远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是买来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我小时候的兴趣就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看见木星卫星的时候真的十分激动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是火星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,章鱼一样的怪物蜿蜒地计划着征服地球的图像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要说好话我也不觉得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是十分友好的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是在地下的大空洞偷偷地生活着的害羞人种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让地球人感到吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑内的火星人到底有多么文雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火星就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来找UFO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在卫星轨道上  一定有异星人的先遣队在待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  实玖瑠也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…呃…UFO  UFO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假还未结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日接着要做的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到击球中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早看见甲子园的新闻我就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能只满足于那些杂牌的棒球比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们SOS团要建成以全国为目标的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那能量到底是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是细胞内的线粒体与常人不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些能量能为世人用上一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  谁也不能阻止春日定下的定额消耗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不停地跟着行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也去了真正的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也将砰砰地射上高空\N又碰碰地绽放的烟花观赏到满足为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在另一天  我们则在县边境的河边参加钓虾虎鱼大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  实玖瑠  竿子竿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  我会拿回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是固定节目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但应该没有人真会去玩的试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看了只有宣传非常像那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但内容大家都心知肚明的大制作电影的联播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在完全是淡季的会漂来水母的海滩上进行海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到所有人都达到全清才能离开的保龄球惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挑战喉咙极限的长时间耐久卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至觉得包括了很多与夏天无关的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我们在这两周内玩到再起不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是8月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,课题都完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀唉呀  总算顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…嗯  也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也好  这个夏天都干了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四处游玩  也穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蝉也抓了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就到这里为止吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这家伙还有什么遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就空下来当是预备日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好好地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后天再在社团教室见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…啊  作业完全没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8月31日  暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正怎么努力都不可能把作业做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法消除玩后的疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这样子拖拖拉拉地过了懒散的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:01.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管了  由它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧  明天还要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关灯睡觉
